effect.silentcompat.amplified.descriptio: Increases speed. Allows certain traits such as Jolt Hit to proc.
effect.silentcompat.devouring.descriptio: Grants absorption hearts on kills. Has a cap. Allows certain traits such as volitile to proc.
effect.silentcompat.restoration.descript: Steadily restores hp over time. Allows certain traits such as scorch to proc.
effect.silentcompat.scorch.description: Sets the target on fire. When the effect ends, the target explodes, spreading scorch to nearby mobs.
trait.silentcompat.abyssal_synergy.desc: Tools deal more damage the deeper you are. Less durability loss the deeper you are.
trait.silentcompat.adrenaline.desc: Briefly applies adrenaline rush when at low health. (Requires: Biomancy)
trait.silentcompat.alf_burst.desc: The Mana Burst is identical to that of a default, unenchanted Alf Blade.
trait.silentcompat.amplifying.desc: Getting a kill has a chance to grant the amplified effect. Requires full set
trait.silentcompat.blinding.desc: Consumes amplified on tool swing, launching a projectile that blinds and slows targets. Damage is equal to 3 times trait level.
trait.silentcompat.chocolate_chipping.de: Chance to drop a chocolate chip on durability loss
trait.silentcompat.corrosive.desc: Briefly applies corrosive to hit targets. (Requires: Biomancy)
trait.silentcompat.devouring.desc: Getting a kill has a chance to grant the devouring effect. Requires full set.
trait.silentcompat.diurnal.desc: Deal increased damage during the day. Gear slowly repairs during the day
trait.silentcompat.dodging.desc: Grants a chance to avoid damage. Requires full armor set. Does not protect against projectiles and armor ignoring damage
trait.silentcompat.emu_dodge.desc: Grants a chance to avoid projectile damage. Requires full armor set
trait.silentcompat.ender_flu.desc: Infects the target with Ender Flu (Requires: Alexs Mobs)
trait.silentcompat.featherweight.desc: Targets take additional knockback when hit. (Requires: Undergarden)
trait.silentcompat.fleetfooted.desc: Increases speed while jumping and sprinting on-hit (Requires: Alexs Mobs)
trait.silentcompat.freezing.desc: Attacks build up freezing on target. At max freeze, damage is dealth over time. Just like stepping in powdered snow. (Requires: Ars Nouveau)
trait.silentcompat.gaia_burst.desc: The Mana Burst is identical to that of a default, unenchanted Mana Stealing Blade.
trait.silentcompat.gooey.desc: Attacks have a chance to apply scintling goo under the target's feet. (Requires: Undergarden
trait.silentcompat.hungering_strike.desc: Deal more damage while under half hunger
trait.silentcompat.jolt_hit.desc: Consumes amplified, dealing bonus damage and chaining to a nearby entity.
trait.silentcompat.knightly.desc: Attacks do extra damage to armored targets
trait.silentcompat.knockout.desc: Chance to inflict a heavy knockback to targets
trait.silentcompat.lava_vision.desc: Provides the Lava Vision effect while in lava. (Requires: Alexs Mobs)
trait.silentcompat.lucky_break.desc: Chance to gain random potion effect when hit. Effected by luck
trait.silentcompat.magnetizing.desc: Magnetizes targets on hit. (Requires: Alex's Caves)
trait.silentcompat.mana_burst.desc: The Mana Burst is identical to that of a default, unenchanted Terra Blade. Uses 100 mana per burst.
trait.silentcompat.mana_repair.desc: Uses 20 + ( 40 per trait level) mana to repair gear. (Requires: Botania)
trait.silentcompat.neptunes_might.desc: Does more damage to targets while in water
trait.silentcompat.nocturnal.desc: Deal increased damage at night. Gear slowly repairs at night
trait.silentcompat.pixie.desc: Pixies may spawn when you are damaged.
trait.silentcompat.purifying.desc: Rare chance to remove harmful effects when hit. Requires full set
trait.silentcompat.restoration.desc: Getting a kill has a chance to grant the restoration effect. Requires full set.
trait.silentcompat.retaliating_blast.des: Attacks or being attacked have a chance to apply a delayed explosion on the target (Requires: Ars Nouveau)
trait.silentcompat.scorching.desc: Consumes restoration, applying the scorch effect to the target hit.
trait.silentcompat.soul_steal.desc: Chance to gain life steal on hit. (Requires: Alexs Mobs)
trait.silentcompat.stunning.desc: Rare chance to stun targets on hit. (Requires: Alex's Caves)
trait.silentcompat.sunspot.desc: Consumes restoration. Standing in fire puts it out, healing a large chunk of health and granting strength.
trait.silentcompat.umbral_blast.desc: Consumes devouring on tool swing, launching a projectile that weakens, damages, and knocks back targets. Damage is equal to 3 times the trait level.
trait.silentcompat.unstable_magic.desc: Somtimes gain a random positive magic effect or apply random negative magic effect to targets. (Requires: Ars Nouveau)
trait.silentcompat.vigorous.desc: Deal more damage while at full health
trait.silentcompat.volatile.desc: Consumes devouring, applying the volatile effect on the target.
trait.silentcompat.vorpal.desc: Deal more damage to targets with over 200 hearts
trait.silentcompat.wither_skull.desc: Summons a wither skull projectile on swing, costing durability.
